He was terrible
to live with, really horrible.

01:16:10.399 --> 01:16:12.276
And with the children
he was snappy

01:16:12.318 --> 01:16:14.446
so I would manage to keep
them out the way.

01:16:15.029 --> 01:16:16.997
Lynsey, don't tear it off!

01:16:24.121 --> 01:16:26.715
He wasn't sleeping,
he was taking sleeping pills.

01:16:26.749 --> 01:16:28.046
He couldn't get to sleep at night.

01:16:28.084 --> 01:16:30.507
He had a rash all over his body.

01:16:30.544 --> 01:16:32.171
And he doesn't tell people this.

01:16:32.213 --> 01:16:35.934
You know, he waits until
it all comes to a head.

