his team to defend properly

01:17:22.429 --> 01:17:24.523
and they go and commit
something like this.

01:17:25.224 --> 01:17:27.272
It's been quite magnificent.

01:17:27.309 --> 01:17:30.062
It's been a night to shake
the soul really.

01:17:30.729 --> 01:17:33.323
<i>If I cannae make decisions</i>

01:17:36.402 --> 01:17:39.952
<i>I said to myself, 'I've got to go.</i> '

